<tt xmlns="http://www.w3.org/ns/ttml" xmlns:amll="http://www.example.com/ns/amll" xmlns:itunes="http://music.apple.com/lyric-ttml-internal" xmlns:ttm="http://www.w3.org/ns/ttml#metadata" itunes:timing="Word"><head><metadata><ttm:agent type="person" xml:id="v1"/><ttm:agent type="other" xml:id="v2"/><amll:meta key="musicName" value="RAJA"/><amll:meta key="musicName" value="RAJA (feat. Mangal Suvarnan)"/><amll:meta key="musicName" value="राजा"/><amll:meta key="musicName" value="王者"/><amll:meta key="musicName" value="RAJA (游戏《无畏契约》特工海神宣传曲)"/><amll:meta key="musicName" value="游戏《无畏契约》特工海神宣传曲"/><amll:meta key="musicName" value="RAJA (王者)"/><amll:meta key="artists" value="VALORANT"/><amll:meta key="artists" value="ARB4"/><amll:meta key="artists" value="Tienas"/><amll:meta key="artists" value="Mangal Suvarnan"/><amll:meta key="artists" value="无畏契约"/><amll:meta key="artists" value="VALORANT Music"/><amll:meta key="album" value="RAJA"/><amll:meta key="album" value="RAJA (feat. Mangal Suvarnan)"/><amll:meta key="album" value="RAJA (feat. Mangal Suvarnan) - Single"/><amll:meta key="album" value="राजा"/><amll:meta key="album" value="RAJA feat. Tienas and Mangal Suvarnan"/><amll:meta key="isrc" value="QZH6S1900639"/><amll:meta key="appleMusicId" value="1831860641"/><amll:meta key="ncmMusicId" value="2081772557"/><amll:meta key="spotifyId" value="2MpRCWHaa8KzG4uXFbYl4v"/><amll:meta key="qqMusicId" value="0024o9pp3HXrSB"/><amll:meta key="ttmlAuthorGithub" value="173352259"/><amll:meta key="ttmlAuthorGithubLogin" value="Zeehan2005"/></metadata></head><body dur="3:41.162"><div begin="14.779" end="3:41.162"><p begin="14.779" end="17.019" itunes:key="L1" ttm:agent="v1"><span begin="14.779" end="15.025">Looking</span> <span begin="15.025" end="15.083">at</span> <span begin="15.083" end="15.297">the</span> <span begin="15.297" end="15.695">world</span> <span begin="15.695" end="15.834">from</span> <span begin="15.834" end="16.039">the</span> <span begin="16.039" end="16.163">eye</span> <span begin="16.163" end="16.344">of</span> <span begin="16.344" end="16.526">the</span> <span begin="16.526" end="17.019">Horus</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-CN">以荷鲁斯之眼俯瞰全场</span></p><p begin="17.134" end="19.570" itunes:key="L2" ttm:agent="v1"><span begin="17.134" end="17.248">If</span> <span begin="17.248" end="17.405">you&apos;re</span> <span begin="17.405" end="17.743">Alex</span><span begin="17.743" end="18.147">ander</span> <span begin="18.147" end="18.248">the</span> <span begin="18.248" end="18.565">Great</span> <span begin="18.658" end="18.819">then</span> <span begin="18.819" end="19.125">I&apos;m</span> <span begin="19.125" end="19.306">the</span> <span begin="19.306" end="19.570">Porus</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-CN">你若为亚历山大大帝，我便是迎击你的波鲁斯王</span></p><p begin="19.886" end="22.401" itunes:key="L3" ttm:agent="v1"><span begin="19.886" end="20.197">Coming</span> <span begin="20.197" end="20.586">straight</span> <span begin="20.586" end="20.725">from</span> <span begin="20.725" end="20.877">the</span> <span begin="20.877" end="21.237">mud,</span> <span begin="21.237" end="21.419">like</span> <span begin="21.577" end="21.949">I&apos;m</span> <span begin="21.949" end="22.099">a</span> <span begin="22.099" end="22.401">lotus</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-CN">自淤泥中破土而生，我如净莲绽放</span></p><p begin="22.401" end="25.626" itunes:key="L4" ttm:agent="v1"><span begin="22.401" end="22.608">100</span> <span begin="22.608" end="23.157">Hathiyon</span> <span begin="23.157" end="23.305">ka</span> <span begin="23.305" end="23.674">bal,</span> <span begin="23.756" end="24.010">kaise</span> <span begin="24.010" end="24.546">sakega</span> <span begin="24.546" end="24.748">tu</span> <span begin="24.748" end="25.050">mujhe</span> <span begin="25.050" end="25.239">rok</span> <span begin="25.239" end="25.626">ab?</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-CN">身具百象巨力，如今你凭何拦我？</span></p><p begin="26.152" end="28.568" itunes:key="L5" ttm:agent="v1"><span begin="26.152" end="26.321">Dekh</span> <span begin="26.321" end="26.504">tu</span> <span begin="26.504" end="26.759">kaise</span> <span begin="26.759" end="26.872">main</span> <span begin="26.872" end="27.140">ladun,</span> <span begin="27.402" end="27.499">tum</span> <span begin="27.499" end="27.712">logon</span> <span begin="27.712" end="27.873">se</span> <span begin="27.873" end="28.158">aise</span> <span begin="28.158" end="28.232">na</span> <span begin="28.232" end="28.568">darun</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-CN">且看我如何鏖战全场，尔等之辈，我何惧分毫</span></p><p begin="28.835" end="31.373" itunes:key="L6" ttm:agent="v1"><span begin="28.835" end="29.132">Taru</span> <span begin="29.132" end="29.298">main</span> <span begin="29.298" end="29.489">jab</span> <span begin="29.489" end="29.554">se</span> <span begin="29.554" end="29.641">main</span> <span begin="29.641" end="29.934">tarun,</span> <span begin="30.008" end="30.196">pani</span> <span begin="30.196" end="30.285">pe</span> <span begin="30.285" end="30.575">calun</span> <span begin="30.575" end="30.657">main,</span> <span begin="30.657" end="30.959">jaise</span> <span begin="30.959" end="31.027">main</span> <span begin="31.027" end="31.373">varun</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-CN">自我扎根之日，便如苍树拔节生长，踏浪而行，我如伐楼拿临世</span></p><p begin="31.715" end="34.130" itunes:key="L7" ttm:agent="v1"><span begin="31.715" end="31.998">Cahe</span> <span begin="31.998" end="32.121">main</span> <span begin="32.121" end="32.416">jiyun</span> <span begin="32.416" end="32.520">ya</span> <span begin="32.520" end="32.782">marun,</span> <span begin="32.782" end="32.911">jo</span> <span begin="32.911" end="33.121">karna</span> <span begin="33.121" end="33.289">cahun</span> <span begin="33.289" end="33.436">main</span> <span begin="33.436" end="33.678">vahi</span> <span begin="33.678" end="33.774">to</span> <span begin="33.774" end="34.130">karun</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-CN">无论我生或死，心之所向，皆可一往无前</span></p><p begin="34.456" end="37.577" itunes:key="L8" ttm:agent="v1"><span begin="34.456" end="34.687">Ata</span> <span begin="34.687" end="34.765">hai</span> <span begin="34.765" end="34.889">tu</span> <span begin="34.889" end="35.102">na</span> <span begin="35.102" end="35.469">qarib,</span> <span begin="35.552" end="35.668">tu</span> <span begin="35.668" end="35.886">bete</span> <span begin="35.886" end="36.103">cikh,</span> <span begin="36.212" end="36.454">jabhi</span> <span begin="36.454" end="36.586">tak</span> <span begin="36.586" end="36.779">kate</span> <span begin="36.779" end="36.957">na</span> <span begin="36.957" end="37.140">teri</span> <span begin="37.140" end="37.320">ye</span> <span begin="37.320" end="37.577">jibh</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-CN">你休想靠近我半步，小子，除非割掉你的烂舌，否则只剩哀嚎不止</span></p><p begin="37.974" end="39.208" itunes:key="L9" ttm:agent="v1"><span begin="37.974" end="38.223">Better</span> <span begin="38.223" end="38.615">believe,</span> <span begin="38.806" end="38.870">you</span> <span begin="38.870" end="39.003">gonna</span> <span begin="39.003" end="39.208">bleed</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-CN">你最好认清现实，你定会血溅当场</span></p><p begin="39.410" end="40.666" itunes:key="L10" ttm:agent="v1"><span begin="39.410" end="39.471">Pick</span> <span begin="39.471" end="39.596">up</span> <span begin="39.596" end="39.692">a</span> <span begin="39.692" end="39.927">seat,</span> <span begin="40.139" end="40.224">get</span> <span begin="40.224" end="40.335">all</span> <span begin="40.335" end="40.472">your</span> <span begin="40.472" end="40.666">team</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-CN">乖乖找好架枪点位，叫上你整支队伍</span></p><p begin="40.822" end="41.760" itunes:key="L11" ttm:agent="v1"><span begin="40.822" end="40.933">I&apos;m</span> <span begin="40.933" end="41.131">the</span> <span begin="41.131" end="41.272">king</span> <span begin="41.272" end="41.398">of</span> <span begin="41.398" end="41.760">kings</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-CN">我是万王之王，纵横战场生死与共</span></p><p begin="42.097" end="43.672" itunes:key="L12" ttm:agent="v1"><span begin="42.097" end="42.328">Brother</span> <span begin="42.328" end="42.543">in</span> <span begin="42.543" end="42.896">arms</span> <span begin="42.896" end="43.035">in</span> <span begin="43.035" end="43.189">a</span> <span begin="43.189" end="43.672">battle</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-CN">纵横战场生死与共</span></p><p begin="43.728" end="46.522" itunes:key="L13" ttm:agent="v1"><span begin="43.728" end="43.903">You</span> <span begin="43.903" end="44.257">all</span> <span begin="44.257" end="44.591">gonna</span> <span begin="44.591" end="44.937">die</span> <span begin="44.937" end="45.070">if</span> <span begin="45.070" end="45.302">you</span> <span begin="45.302" end="45.654">act</span> <span begin="45.654" end="45.801">like</span> <span begin="45.801" end="45.976">a</span> <span begin="45.976" end="46.522">Vandal</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-CN">你若像持狂徒乱冲的莽夫般肆意妄为，下场唯有死路一条</span></p><p begin="46.852" end="49.387" itunes:key="L14" ttm:agent="v1"><span begin="46.852" end="46.992">Bring</span> <span begin="46.992" end="47.073">the</span> <span begin="47.073" end="47.417">realm</span> <span begin="47.417" end="47.603">to</span> <span begin="47.603" end="48.285">reality</span> <span begin="48.285" end="48.449">from</span> <span begin="48.449" end="48.794">every</span> <span begin="48.794" end="49.387">angle</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-CN">从四面八方，将神域之力拉入现世</span></p><p begin="50.361" end="54.970" itunes:key="L15" ttm:agent="v1"><span begin="50.361" end="50.485">This</span> <span begin="50.485" end="50.668">is</span> <span begin="50.668" end="50.850">the</span> <span begin="50.850" end="51.237">public</span> <span begin="51.237" end="51.579">service</span> <span begin="51.579" end="52.230">announce</span><span begin="52.230" end="52.525">ment</span> <span begin="52.525" end="52.686">from</span> <span begin="52.686" end="53.121">Mumbai</span> <span begin="53.121" end="53.394">to</span> <span begin="53.394" end="53.510">the</span> <span begin="53.510" end="53.696">rest</span> <span begin="53.696" end="53.969">of</span> <span begin="53.969" end="54.218">the</span> <span begin="54.218" end="54.970">world</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-CN">这是从孟买，向全世界发布的宣告</span></p><p begin="55.554" end="57.777" itunes:key="L16" ttm:agent="v1"><span begin="55.554" end="55.761">I</span> <span begin="55.761" end="56.117">am</span> <span begin="56.350" end="56.525">a</span> <span begin="56.525" end="57.441">raja,</span> <span begin="57.655" end="57.777">uh</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-CN">我乃一代君王，uh</span></p><p begin="59.877" end="1:01.540" itunes:key="L17" ttm:agent="v1"><span begin="59.877" end="1:00.271">I</span> <span begin="1:00.271" end="1:00.448">am</span> <span begin="1:00.448" end="1:00.685">the</span> <span begin="1:00.685" end="1:01.540">raja</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-CN">我乃万王之王</span></p><p begin="1:02.115" end="1:05.381" itunes:key="L18" ttm:agent="v1"><span begin="1:02.115" end="1:02.607">Bhidega</span> <span begin="1:02.607" end="1:02.845">to</span> <span begin="1:02.845" end="1:03.337">uthega</span> <span begin="1:03.337" end="1:04.195">janaza</span> <span begin="1:04.195" end="1:05.381">na</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-CN">敢与我为敌，便等着抬棺出殡</span></p><p begin="1:05.381" end="1:07.154" itunes:key="L19" ttm:agent="v1"><span begin="1:05.381" end="1:05.515">Tu</span> <span begin="1:05.515" end="1:05.879">meri</span> <span begin="1:05.879" end="1:06.302">taraf</span> <span begin="1:06.302" end="1:06.583">a</span> <span begin="1:06.583" end="1:07.154">na</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-CN">你若敢朝我走来</span></p><p begin="1:07.537" end="1:11.020" itunes:key="L20" ttm:agent="v1"><span begin="1:07.537" end="1:07.775">A</span> <span begin="1:07.775" end="1:08.178">gaya</span> <span begin="1:08.178" end="1:08.338">to</span> <span begin="1:08.338" end="1:08.692">hoga</span> <span begin="1:08.692" end="1:08.904">phir</span> <span begin="1:08.904" end="1:09.678">tanaza</span> <span begin="1:09.678" end="1:11.020">na</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-CN">踏来的那一刻，便只剩粉身碎骨</span></p><p begin="1:11.020" end="1:12.691" itunes:key="L21" ttm:agent="v1"><span begin="1:11.020" end="1:11.171">Ye</span> <span begin="1:11.171" end="1:11.832">bharatiy</span> <span begin="1:11.832" end="1:12.691">bhasa</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-CN">这是印度的语言</span></p><p begin="1:12.908" end="1:16.357" itunes:key="L22" ttm:agent="v1"><span begin="1:12.908" end="1:13.128">Phir</span> <span begin="1:13.128" end="1:13.721">duniya</span> <span begin="1:13.721" end="1:14.244">sunegi</span> <span begin="1:14.244" end="1:14.434">ye</span> <span begin="1:14.434" end="1:15.268">tarana</span> <span begin="1:15.268" end="1:16.357">na</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-CN">全世界终将听见这首战歌</span></p><p begin="1:16.548" end="1:18.215" itunes:key="L23" ttm:agent="v1"><span begin="1:16.548" end="1:16.692">&apos;Cause</span> <span begin="1:16.692" end="1:17.051">I</span> <span begin="1:17.051" end="1:17.236">am</span> <span begin="1:17.236" end="1:17.388">the</span> <span begin="1:17.388" end="1:18.215">raja</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-CN">只因我乃万王之王</span></p><p begin="1:19.309" end="1:21.604" itunes:key="L24" ttm:agent="v1"><span begin="1:19.309" end="1:19.453">&apos;Cause</span> <span begin="1:19.453" end="1:19.761">I</span> <span begin="1:19.761" end="1:20.023">am</span> <span begin="1:20.023" end="1:20.191">the</span> <span begin="1:20.191" end="1:21.604">raja</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-CN">只因我乃万王之王</span></p><p begin="1:26.568" end="1:27.283" itunes:key="L25" ttm:agent="v1"><span begin="1:26.568" end="1:26.812">I</span> <span begin="1:26.812" end="1:26.975">am</span> <span begin="1:26.975" end="1:27.283">the...</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-CN">我就是…</span></p><p begin="1:30.531" end="1:32.756" itunes:key="L26" ttm:agent="v1"><span begin="1:30.531" end="1:30.696">&apos;Cause</span> <span begin="1:30.696" end="1:30.945">I</span> <span begin="1:30.945" end="1:31.128">am</span> <span begin="1:31.128" end="1:31.331">the</span> <span begin="1:31.331" end="1:32.756">raja</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-CN">只因我乃万王之王</span></p><p begin="1:37.644" end="1:38.435" itunes:key="L27" ttm:agent="v1"><span begin="1:37.644" end="1:37.979">I</span> <span begin="1:37.979" end="1:38.242">am</span> <span begin="1:38.242" end="1:38.435">the...</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-CN">我就是…</span></p><p begin="1:41.657" end="1:43.980" itunes:key="L28" ttm:agent="v1"><span begin="1:41.657" end="1:41.784">&apos;Cause</span> <span begin="1:41.784" end="1:42.136">I</span> <span begin="1:42.136" end="1:42.344">am</span> <span begin="1:42.344" end="1:42.558">the</span> <span begin="1:42.558" end="1:43.980">raja</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-CN">只因我乃万王之王</span></p><p begin="1:49.921" end="1:52.263" itunes:key="L29" ttm:agent="v1"><span begin="1:49.921" end="1:49.998">Look</span> <span begin="1:49.998" end="1:50.067">in</span> <span begin="1:50.067" end="1:50.130">my</span> <span begin="1:50.130" end="1:50.569">eyes,</span> <span begin="1:50.569" end="1:50.713">what</span> <span begin="1:50.713" end="1:50.791">do</span> <span begin="1:50.791" end="1:50.932">you</span> <span begin="1:50.932" end="1:51.025">see?</span> <span begin="1:51.025" end="1:51.231">I&apos;m</span> <span begin="1:51.231" end="1:51.374">more</span> <span begin="1:51.374" end="1:51.533">than</span> <span begin="1:51.533" end="1:51.709">an</span> <span begin="1:51.709" end="1:51.892">average</span> <span begin="1:51.892" end="1:52.263">man</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-CN">凝视我的双眼，你看见了什么？ 我绝非凡夫俗子</span></p><p begin="1:52.413" end="1:55.033" itunes:key="L30" ttm:agent="v1"><span begin="1:52.413" end="1:52.583">I&apos;m</span> <span begin="1:52.583" end="1:52.666">a</span> <span begin="1:52.666" end="1:53.158">maverick,</span> <span begin="1:53.158" end="1:53.303">I</span> <span begin="1:53.303" end="1:53.482">can</span> <span begin="1:53.482" end="1:53.647">grow</span> <span begin="1:53.647" end="1:54.004">flowers</span> <span begin="1:54.004" end="1:54.174">on</span> <span begin="1:54.174" end="1:54.351">a</span> <span begin="1:54.351" end="1:54.686">barren</span> <span begin="1:54.686" end="1:55.033">land</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-CN">我是逆势破局的独行者，能于不毛之地生花</span></p><p begin="1:55.462" end="1:57.567" itunes:key="L31" ttm:agent="v1"><span begin="1:55.462" end="1:55.588">Break</span> <span begin="1:55.588" end="1:55.773">a</span> <span begin="1:55.773" end="1:56.125">mountain</span> <span begin="1:56.125" end="1:56.263">with</span> <span begin="1:56.263" end="1:56.423">my</span> <span begin="1:56.423" end="1:56.625">bare</span> <span begin="1:56.625" end="1:56.979">hands</span> <span begin="1:56.979" end="1:57.147">and</span> <span begin="1:57.147" end="1:57.394">step</span> <span begin="1:57.394" end="1:57.567">back</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-CN">赤手空拳劈开山峦，从容抽身</span></p><p begin="1:57.672" end="2:00.647" itunes:key="L32" ttm:agent="v1"><span begin="1:57.672" end="1:57.831">And</span> <span begin="1:57.831" end="1:58.076">cause</span> <span begin="1:58.076" end="1:58.208">a</span> <span begin="1:58.208" end="1:58.542">literal</span> <span begin="1:58.542" end="1:59.245">avalanche,</span> <span begin="1:59.245" end="1:59.282">shoot</span> <span begin="1:59.282" end="1:59.382">a</span> <span begin="1:59.382" end="1:59.564">bullet</span> <span begin="1:59.564" end="1:59.751">while</span> <span begin="1:59.751" end="1:59.921">it&apos;s</span> <span begin="1:59.921" end="2:00.647">traveling</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-CN">抬手便引山崩地裂，子弹飞驰之际，我仍能精准扣动扳机</span></p><p begin="2:00.785" end="2:03.366" itunes:key="L33" ttm:agent="v1"><span begin="2:00.785" end="2:01.100">Ast</span> <span begin="2:01.100" end="2:01.744">bhujaye</span> <span begin="2:01.744" end="2:02.115">meri</span> <span begin="2:02.115" end="2:02.461">jaise</span> <span begin="2:02.461" end="2:02.706">main</span> <span begin="2:02.706" end="2:03.366">tarantula</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-CN">我身具八臂，如狼蛛般锋芒难挡</span></p><p begin="2:03.366" end="2:06.214" itunes:key="L34" ttm:agent="v1"><span begin="2:03.366" end="2:03.535">Na</span> <span begin="2:03.535" end="2:03.685">hai</span> <span begin="2:03.685" end="2:03.815">koi</span> <span begin="2:03.815" end="2:04.038">tor</span> <span begin="2:04.038" end="2:04.482">mera</span> <span begin="2:04.482" end="2:04.641">jab</span> <span begin="2:04.641" end="2:04.832">se</span> <span begin="2:04.832" end="2:05.193">purvajon</span> <span begin="2:05.193" end="2:05.524">gyan</span> <span begin="2:05.524" end="2:06.214">mila</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-CN">自先祖传承远古智慧，我便无坚不摧、毫无破绽</span></p><p begin="2:06.604" end="2:09.006" itunes:key="L35" ttm:agent="v1"><span begin="2:06.604" end="2:06.927">Mere</span> <span begin="2:06.927" end="2:07.272">jaisa</span> <span begin="2:07.272" end="2:07.783">milega</span> <span begin="2:07.783" end="2:08.159">koi</span> <span begin="2:08.159" end="2:08.329">na,</span> <span begin="2:08.329" end="2:08.484">tu</span> <span begin="2:08.484" end="2:08.673">aur,</span> <span begin="2:08.673" end="2:08.824">tu</span> <span begin="2:08.824" end="2:09.006">aur</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-CN">普天之下，无人能与我比肩，尔等皆为蝼蚁</span></p><p begin="2:09.006" end="2:11.364" itunes:key="L36" ttm:agent="v1"><span begin="2:09.006" end="2:09.341">Cahe</span> <span begin="2:09.341" end="2:09.495">jo</span> <span begin="2:09.495" end="2:09.734">bhi</span> <span begin="2:09.734" end="2:09.928">tha,</span> <span begin="2:09.928" end="2:10.324">sabki</span> <span begin="2:10.324" end="2:10.598">qabar</span> <span begin="2:10.598" end="2:10.932">mainne</span> <span begin="2:10.932" end="2:11.364">khodi</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-CN">无论曾经何等风光，皆被我亲手送入坟墓</span></p><p begin="2:11.364" end="2:13.705" itunes:key="L37" ttm:agent="v1"><span begin="2:11.364" end="2:11.549">Kya</span> <span begin="2:11.549" end="2:11.639">tum</span> <span begin="2:11.639" end="2:12.228">lagaoge</span> <span begin="2:12.228" end="2:12.694">boliyan,</span> <span begin="2:12.694" end="2:12.790">kam</span> <span begin="2:12.790" end="2:13.192">paren</span> <span begin="2:13.192" end="2:13.705">goliyan</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-CN">你以为口舌之利能伤我？连子弹都不足以撼我分毫</span></p><p begin="2:13.705" end="2:16.372" itunes:key="L38" ttm:agent="v1"><span begin="2:13.705" end="2:14.421">Chandragupta</span> <span begin="2:14.421" end="2:14.577">main</span> <span begin="2:14.577" end="2:15.077">Maurya,</span> <span begin="2:15.077" end="2:15.231">yad</span> <span begin="2:15.231" end="2:15.597">dila</span> <span begin="2:15.597" end="2:15.791">dun</span> <span begin="2:15.791" end="2:16.372">loriyan</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-CN">我便是旃陀罗笈多·孔雀，我会用摇篮曲送你长眠</span></p><p begin="2:16.372" end="2:19.286" itunes:key="L39" ttm:agent="v1"><span begin="2:16.372" end="2:16.506">Come</span> <span begin="2:16.506" end="2:16.686">to</span> <span begin="2:16.686" end="2:16.886">me</span> <span begin="2:16.886" end="2:17.040">and</span> <span begin="2:17.040" end="2:17.216">you</span> <span begin="2:17.216" end="2:17.418">just</span> <span begin="2:17.418" end="2:17.739">gonna</span> <span begin="2:17.739" end="2:18.072">die,</span> <span begin="2:18.072" end="2:18.263">that&apos;s</span> <span begin="2:18.263" end="2:18.582">really</span> <span begin="2:18.582" end="2:18.816">a</span> <span begin="2:18.816" end="2:19.286">given</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-CN">敢靠近我，唯有死路一条，这是板上钉钉的结局</span></p><p begin="2:19.416" end="2:23.275" itunes:key="L40" ttm:agent="v1"><span begin="2:19.416" end="2:19.625">I</span> <span begin="2:19.625" end="2:19.851">am</span> <span begin="2:19.851" end="2:20.201">in</span><span begin="2:20.201" end="2:20.358">vin</span><span begin="2:20.358" end="2:20.574">ci</span><span begin="2:20.574" end="2:20.674">ble</span> <span begin="2:20.674" end="2:20.846">and</span> <span begin="2:20.846" end="2:21.180">you&apos;re</span> <span begin="2:21.180" end="2:21.575">in</span><span begin="2:21.575" end="2:21.736">vi</span><span begin="2:21.736" end="2:21.892">si</span><span begin="2:21.892" end="2:22.037">ble,</span> <span begin="2:22.037" end="2:22.281">see</span> <span begin="2:22.281" end="2:22.547">that&apos;s</span> <span begin="2:22.547" end="2:22.825">really</span> <span begin="2:22.825" end="2:22.988">a</span> <span begin="2:22.988" end="2:23.275">difference</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-CN">我所向披靡，而你不值一提，这便是我们之间的天壤之别</span></p><p begin="2:23.536" end="2:26.117" itunes:key="L41" ttm:agent="v1"><span begin="2:23.536" end="2:23.663">Get</span> <span begin="2:23.663" end="2:23.830">out</span> <span begin="2:23.830" end="2:23.986">of</span> <span begin="2:23.986" end="2:24.171">my</span> <span begin="2:24.171" end="2:24.342">way</span> <span begin="2:24.342" end="2:24.507">or</span> <span begin="2:24.507" end="2:24.686">leave</span> <span begin="2:24.686" end="2:24.859">the</span> <span begin="2:24.859" end="2:25.020">world,</span> <span begin="2:25.020" end="2:25.203">the</span> <span begin="2:25.203" end="2:25.552">choice</span> <span begin="2:25.552" end="2:25.706">is</span> <span begin="2:25.706" end="2:26.117">yours</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-CN">给我滚开，或是离开这个世界，你自己选</span></p><p begin="2:26.336" end="2:29.521" itunes:key="L42" ttm:agent="v1"><span begin="2:26.336" end="2:26.479">I</span> <span begin="2:26.479" end="2:26.650">don&apos;t</span> <span begin="2:26.650" end="2:26.823">kill</span> <span begin="2:26.823" end="2:26.996">my</span> <span begin="2:26.996" end="2:27.336">enemies</span> <span begin="2:27.336" end="2:27.498">I</span> <span begin="2:27.498" end="2:27.688">play</span> <span begin="2:27.688" end="2:27.859">with</span> <span begin="2:27.859" end="2:28.070">them,</span> <span begin="2:28.070" end="2:28.229">that&apos;s</span> <span begin="2:28.229" end="2:28.418">what</span> <span begin="2:28.418" end="2:28.587">the</span> <span begin="2:28.587" end="2:28.931">toys</span> <span begin="2:28.931" end="2:29.132">are</span> <span begin="2:29.132" end="2:29.521">for</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-CN">我从不直接斩杀敌人，只会戏耍他们，玩具本就该这么用</span></p><p begin="2:31.703" end="2:34.138" itunes:key="L43" ttm:agent="v1"><span begin="2:31.703" end="2:31.765">From</span> <span begin="2:31.765" end="2:31.989">Mumbai</span> <span begin="2:31.989" end="2:32.433">to</span> <span begin="2:32.433" end="2:32.594">the</span> <span begin="2:32.594" end="2:32.760">rest</span> <span begin="2:32.760" end="2:33.131">of</span> <span begin="2:33.131" end="2:33.307">the</span> <span begin="2:33.307" end="2:34.138">world</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-CN">从孟买，向全世界宣告</span></p><p begin="2:34.880" end="2:36.543" itunes:key="L44" ttm:agent="v1"><span begin="2:34.880" end="2:35.274">I</span> <span begin="2:35.274" end="2:35.451">am</span> <span begin="2:35.451" end="2:35.688">the</span> <span begin="2:35.688" end="2:36.543">raja</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-CN">我乃万王之王</span></p><p begin="2:37.118" end="2:40.384" itunes:key="L45" ttm:agent="v1"><span begin="2:37.118" end="2:37.610">Bhidega</span> <span begin="2:37.610" end="2:37.848">to</span> <span begin="2:37.848" end="2:38.340">uthega</span> <span begin="2:38.340" end="2:39.198">janaza</span> <span begin="2:39.198" end="2:40.384">na</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-CN">敢与我为敌，便等着抬棺出殡</span></p><p begin="2:40.384" end="2:42.157" itunes:key="L46" ttm:agent="v1"><span begin="2:40.384" end="2:40.518">Tu</span> <span begin="2:40.518" end="2:40.882">meri</span> <span begin="2:40.882" end="2:41.305">taraf</span> <span begin="2:41.305" end="2:41.586">a</span> <span begin="2:41.586" end="2:42.157">na</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-CN">你若敢朝我走来</span></p><p begin="2:42.540" end="2:46.023" itunes:key="L47" ttm:agent="v1"><span begin="2:42.540" end="2:42.778">A</span> <span begin="2:42.778" end="2:43.181">gaya</span> <span begin="2:43.181" end="2:43.341">to</span> <span begin="2:43.341" end="2:43.695">hoga</span> <span begin="2:43.695" end="2:43.907">phir</span> <span begin="2:43.907" end="2:44.681">tanaza</span> <span begin="2:44.681" end="2:46.023">na</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-CN">踏来的那一刻，便只剩粉身碎骨</span></p><p begin="2:46.023" end="2:47.694" itunes:key="L48" ttm:agent="v1"><span begin="2:46.023" end="2:46.174">Ye</span> <span begin="2:46.174" end="2:46.835">bharatiy</span> <span begin="2:46.835" end="2:47.694">bhasa</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-CN">这是印度的语言</span></p><p begin="2:47.911" end="2:51.360" itunes:key="L49" ttm:agent="v1"><span begin="2:47.911" end="2:48.131">Phir</span> <span begin="2:48.131" end="2:48.724">duniya</span> <span begin="2:48.724" end="2:49.247">sunegi</span> <span begin="2:49.247" end="2:49.437">ye</span> <span begin="2:49.437" end="2:50.271">tarana</span> <span begin="2:50.271" end="2:51.360">na</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-CN">全世界终将听见这首战歌</span></p><p begin="2:51.551" end="2:53.218" itunes:key="L50" ttm:agent="v1"><span begin="2:51.551" end="2:51.695">&apos;Cause</span> <span begin="2:51.695" end="2:52.054">I</span> <span begin="2:52.054" end="2:52.239">am</span> <span begin="2:52.239" end="2:52.391">the</span> <span begin="2:52.391" end="2:53.218">raja</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-CN">只因我乃万王之王</span></p><p begin="2:54.312" end="2:56.607" itunes:key="L51" ttm:agent="v1"><span begin="2:54.312" end="2:54.456">&apos;Cause</span> <span begin="2:54.456" end="2:54.764">I</span> <span begin="2:54.764" end="2:55.026">am</span> <span begin="2:55.026" end="2:55.194">the</span> <span begin="2:55.194" end="2:56.607">raja</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-CN">只因我乃万王之王</span></p><p begin="3:01.571" end="3:02.286" itunes:key="L52" ttm:agent="v1"><span begin="3:01.571" end="3:01.815">I</span> <span begin="3:01.815" end="3:01.978">am</span> <span begin="3:01.978" end="3:02.286">the...</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-CN">我就是…</span></p><p begin="3:05.534" end="3:07.658" itunes:key="L53" ttm:agent="v1"><span begin="3:05.534" end="3:05.699">&apos;Cause</span> <span begin="3:05.699" end="3:05.948">I</span> <span begin="3:05.948" end="3:06.131">am</span> <span begin="3:06.131" end="3:06.334">the</span> <span begin="3:06.334" end="3:07.658">raja</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-CN">只因我乃万王之王</span></p><p begin="3:07.659" end="3:10.210" itunes:key="L54" ttm:agent="v2"><span begin="3:07.659" end="3:07.798">Put</span> <span begin="3:07.798" end="3:07.953">your</span> <span begin="3:07.953" end="3:08.316">back</span> <span begin="3:08.316" end="3:08.731">down</span> <span begin="3:08.731" end="3:08.929">on</span> <span begin="3:08.929" end="3:09.057">your</span> <span begin="3:09.057" end="3:09.377">knees,</span> <span begin="3:09.377" end="3:09.524">won&apos;t</span> <span begin="3:09.524" end="3:09.710">you</span> <span begin="3:09.710" end="3:09.861">kiss</span> <span begin="3:09.861" end="3:10.041">the</span> <span begin="3:10.041" end="3:10.210">ring?</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-CN">双膝跪地，亲吻我的权戒，如何？</span></p><p begin="3:10.210" end="3:12.433" itunes:key="L55" ttm:agent="v2"><span begin="3:10.210" end="3:10.436">Now</span> <span begin="3:10.436" end="3:10.481">put</span> <span begin="3:10.481" end="3:10.725">your</span> <span begin="3:10.725" end=